<p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>



<p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;font-size:20px;color:#405e8e;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'><strong>&nbsp;2. Information We Collect &nbsp;</strong></p>
<p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'><strong>We collect the following types of information from you to provide and improve our services, enhance your experience, and ensure compliance with legal obligations:<br>
• Personal Information: Name, email address, phone number, and student status (college affiliation).<br>
• Payment Information: Processed through a secure third-party; not stored by us.<br>
• Usage Data: Deals viewed, redeemed, and user preferences.<br>
• Device Information: Device type, operating system, and IP address.<br>
• Location Data: If permission is granted, we collect location-based data to enhance deal recommendations.<br>
• Cookies: Cookies and tracking technologies are used to improve app functionality and deliver personalized services.<br>
 &nbsp;</strong></p>
 
 


<p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;font-size:20px;color:#405e8e;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'><strong>&nbsp;3. How We Use Your Information &nbsp;</strong></p>
<p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'><strong>The information we collect is used to:<br>
