• Comply with applicable laws.<br>
• Analyze user trends to improve app features and performance.<br>
&nbsp;</strong></p>


<p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;font-size:20px;color:#405e8e;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'><strong>&nbsp;4. Sharing Your Information &nbsp;</strong></p>
