• Service Providers: For payment processing, customer support, and app functionality.<br>
• Legal Compliance: When required by law or court order.<br>
• Business Transfers: In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale.<br>
• With Your Consent: When you give explicit permission.<br>
</strong></p>



<p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;font-size:20px;color:#405e8e;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'><strong><br>&nbsp;5. Security of Your Information &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'><strong>We employ industry-standard security measures, including:<br>
• Encryption: Ensuring sensitive data is encrypted during transmission and storage.<br>
• Access Controls: Restricting access to authorized personnel only.<br>
• Data Retention: Retaining your data for the necessary period to provide services or as required by law.<br>
Despite these precautions, no system is completely secure. In case of a data breach, we will notify affected users as required by law.<br>
</strong></p>

<p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;font-size:20px;color:#405e8e;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'><strong><br>&nbsp;6. Your Rights and Choices &nbsp;</strong></p>
